info.name: Collect & Verything
info.description:
An Laravel API RESTful application that serves as the backend for the Collect & Verything application. It is built using the Laravel framework and follows the RESTful API conventions. # Documentation üìö - [Getting Started](#getting-started-) üöÄ - [Requirements](#requirements-) üìã - [System Requirements](#system-requirements-) üñ•Ô∏è - [Installation](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/INSTALLATION.md) üíæ - [Usage](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md) üîß - [API Documentation](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#api-documentation-) üìñ - [API Endpoints](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#api-endpoints-) üì° - [Authentication](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#authentication-) üîê - [Admin](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#admin-) üõ°Ô∏è - [Users](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#users-) üë§ - [Roles](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#roles-) üé≠ - [Addresses](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#addresses-) üè† - [Postman](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/USAGE.md#postman-) üì¨ - [Tests](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/docs/TESTS.md) üß™ ## Getting Started üöÄ Welcome to the Fiches Pedagogiques API RESTful application. This application serves as the backend for the Collect & Verything application. It is built using the Laravel framework and follows the RESTful API conventions. ### Requirements üìã #### System Requirements üñ•Ô∏è - PHP >= 8.2.x - Composer - Docker (may be optional) Visual Studio Code Extensions: - PHP Intelephense ## Contributing ü§ù Please read the [contributing guide](https://github.com/DevGenius-IT/collect-n-verything-back/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md). ## Project üìÇ We have organized our work into a single project to streamline development and ensure clarity. You can follow the progress and contribute through the link below: - [API - Collect & Verything Project](https://github.com/orgs/DevGenius-IT/projects/2) ---


Copyright ¬© 2024-present@DevGenius-IT

| Name      | Method    | Path                     | Parameters                                                                                                                                                                         | Headers  | Description            |
| --------- | --------- | ------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- | ---------------------- |
| Index     | üü¢ GET    | `/admin/users`           | `limit`, `page`, `order`, `orderBy`, `trash`                                                                                                                                       | `fields` | Get all users          |
| Show      | üü¢ GET    | `/admin/users/{id}`      |                                                                                                                                                                                    | `fields` | Get a user by ID       |
| Store     | üü° POST   | `/admin/users`           | `firstname`, `lastname`, `username`, `email`, `password`, `password_confirmation`, `roles`, `phone_number `, `has_newsletter`, `has_commercials`, `has_thematic_alerts`, `advantage_number`, `school_id`, `address_id`, `workplace_id`, `sections`, `shops`, `user_types`      |          | Create a new user      |

| Destroy   | üî¥ DELETE | `/admin/users`           | `ids`, `force`                                                                                                                                                                     |          | Delete multiple users  |
| Restore   | üü£ PATCH  | `/admin/users/restore`   | `ids`                                                                                                                                                                              |          | Restore multiple users |
| Duplicate | üü£ PATCH  | `/admin/users/duplicate` | [`duplicate_from` and user fields]                                                                                                                                                 |          | Duplicate a user       |
